***** Course Description *****
This calculus course covers differentiation and integration of functions of one
variable, and concludes with a brief discussion of infinite series. Calculus is
fundamental to many scientific disciplines including physics, engineering, and
economics.
*** Course Format ***
===============================================================================
[Click_to_get_started.]This course has been designed for independent study. It
includes all of the materials you will need to understand the concepts covered
in this subject. The materials in this course include:
    * Lecture Videos with supporting written notes
    * Recitation Videos of problem-solving tips
    * Worked Examples with detailed solutions to sample problems
    * Problem sets with solutions
    * Exams with solutions
    * Interactive Java Applets ("Mathlets") to reinforce key concepts
    * An Online Study Group
